ne. *smile*</p><br><p align="center"><b><font size="4"><u>~: :~ Requirements to join ~: :~</u></font></b></p><br><p align="left"><br><br>  The level limit for applying to "<a href="http://www.thetwelve.org" target="_blank">Legendary Twelve</a>" is 55. Melee ( Tank ) Classes will need to be 58 .</p><br><p>We do ask that you have your epic or better at this time but, that will be taken into consideration also if you do not have your epic depending on class and how far you are into your epic.</p><br><p>We look forward to meeting you all ingame and thanks again for stopping by the site!</p><br><p><b>Our Rules for Membership: </b>We do require you to join our guild on raids, exp groups etc. Anything for you to get familiar with our guildies and vice versa.</p><br><p>We have a 30 day probation period once you are guilded for further evaluation of your abilities. At the end of the 30 days there is a vote taken to deem if you are "Legendary Twelve" material. During this 30 day probation period there is a 2 week NO LOOT period. This means during this 2 weeks new members can not participate in the loot drops during guild raids. There are some minor exceptions to this rule which we will discuss at the time this comes up.</p><br><p>We are on a DKP ( Points System ). Once your 2 week period is up you are allowed to use your points for items you wish, with certain exceptions of our "Wish List" system which you can read more about on our web page <a href="http://www.thetwelve.org" target="_blank">Legendary Twelve</a>.</p><br><p>If you agree with the rules above please feel free to post an application for review. </p><br><p align="center"><b>********</b></p><br><p>After you post we move your app to our private recruit discussion section so please know that we *are* listening and your post didn't poof for no reason  =)</p><br><p>Feel free to contact an officer ... Cinexa, Teuen or Snaggle with questions on the status<br> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub72.ezboa